lastCommitMessage: chore: update dependencies and enhance chat functionality
- Updated the agora_market_dart_sdk dependency reference in pubspec.yaml to the latest commit.
- Refactored chat message retrieval logic in admin_message_page.dart and chat_view.dart to include sessionId in query parameters for improved message fetching.
- Added logging statements in chat_view.dart to track session initialization, message loading, and file upload processes, enhancing debugging capabilities.
- Removed redundant logging in product_list_page.dart to streamline the codebase.
